## CI Failure Analysis Summary

| Repo | Failure | Status | Fix Applied |
|------|---------|--------|-------------|
| **Root** | Submodule `docs` points to stale commit (`02c0fab...`) | ✅ Fixed | Synced submodules and pushed |
| **Frontend** | TypeScript errors in test mocks | ✅ Already Fixed | `bun typecheck` passes |
| **Server** | PostgreSQL/Redis required but CI uses SQLite | ⚠️ Infrastructure | Needs CI to provide real DB/Redis |
